Hiya everyone! I would say I'm new here, but I'm not exactly, I've bene here
before, some of you might remember me.. I hope. LOL Umm anyway, I'm just
saying Hi! to Zardus and Airshadow Nightlight!! *waves madly*.

Also, could someone, like, find me? LOL I don't exactly wanna start out an
RPG with no-one to RPG -with-. :D

I'll attach my profile down the bottom.. *_*

~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~

The gentle silence of the night was broken sharply by the sound of a Status
Pod suddenly zipping through the sky and crash landing on the soft Earth.
Birds squawked and flew off, startled, and flapped their way to a possibly
more peaceful area.

The moonlight reflected off the polished metal, only marred by a slight dirt
scrape. The DNA scanner opened the panel and slid upwards, sending out an
electronic wave.

::DNA found:: It reported, and slid back into the Pod. It clicked and
whirred for a few minutes, then the lid cracked open with a hiss. A shadow
climbed out, it's movements cautious.

What little light there was showed a dark black panther, with silver/black
wings attached to it's shoulder blades. Her emerald green eyes glittered in
the low light, and she darted a few quick looks around her to make sure she
wasn't going to be attack or anything like that.

A glimmer of light caught her Maximal mark, but she found herself wondering
why she was with the Maximals. The last time she was here, they had bene led
by Liono Prime. The bot smirked a little, and sat down in her Panther/Hawk
mode, waiting a little before she could travel.

~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~*~

Name: Teltoli SilverWing

Gender: Female

Beast Mode Characteristics: As a Panther/Hawk Fuzor, Teltoli has the body of
a panther, with silver 'socks' on her four paws. Her eyes are emerald green.
From her shoulder blades are two large wings, also black with silver marks.

Bot Mode Characteristics: In her Bot mode, Teltoli is also black with green
eyes, and silver on her arms that look like elbow-length gloves, and silver
ringlets on her ankles. She is very pretty, in a girlish sort of way. Her
faded gray Maximal mark is on the outside top of her right leg. Her face is
faintly cat-tish, with the two rounded ears on top of her head, and faint
whisker marks. Her black wings also stay on her back in Bot Mode, so she can
fly.

Weapons: The panther tail turns into a whip with a long scythe-like blade at
the end. From her wings, come two long rapiers that she can use with deadly
accuracy.

Personality: Teltoli is a kind, caring Bot, easy to love and be loved with
all her heart, and acts a lot like a small child in the way of innocence.
But sometimes that gets her in trouble when she's in battle. However, once
she is fired up for a fight, she will go down to the end for her friends and
leader.
Her father was a great warrior, and taught her many of his moves, and her
mother taught her others things, like healing with herbs when one was
running low on power.

------------------
Teltoli SilverWing
Panther/Hawk Fuzor
